{"tid":952903,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"多款低價 iPad 2019 年登場！iPad mini 5 及 iphone se2消息來了！","createTime":"2018-12-23T13:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T08:06:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"137d84b67c39c37f0f7632b3b5c334cb00d3491b","tid":952903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:56:17.000Z","msg":"By 聖騎士 - Dec 22, 2018<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018 年，蘋果主力在高端的 iPad Pro 作出改革，也許 2019 年的重點會改為入門級低價 iPad 了！來自《中國時報》的報導指蘋果 2019 年將推出新 iPad mini 及將 9.7 吋版 iPad 改版。<br />\n<br />\n2 年沒有更新過的 7.9. iPad mini 將推出新版，供應鏈預計 12 月底量產，預計 2019 年上半年推出。而 2018 年的 iPad 9.7 吋性價比很高，而消息指 2019 年會對入門版的 iPad 再作出改革，邊框比現時更窄，從而螢幕會變成 10 吋以上，預計最快要 2019 年中才量產，會在 2019 下半年上市。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市場預期，iPad mini 定位是入門級平板，會換上新處理器但仍保留 Touch ID。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/12/22/ipad-mini-5-ipad2019-info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F12%2F22%2Fipad-mini-5-ipad2019-info%2F&d=dzXL1%2FGw5IWxb47Be3UjhjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=43006a6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/12/22/ipad-mini-5-ipad2019-info/</a>"},{"pid":"eaa240022ebd07ec7170a3d42de2f4a5833e3a02","tid":952903,"uid":46527,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:59:07.000Z","msg":"信一半先"},{"pid":"6f03468f8530484501b062df4e8f80f7b5fc1946","tid":952903,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":94,"score":-91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"90b356d2a6ae383628051b7e29506295893b1f65","tid":952903,"uid":6313,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">入門級低價 iPad </span><br />\n新Macbook Air同iPhone XR咪又係話平價<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b004b03928138677114a8244612ccc0fb88ffd","tid":952903,"uid":80103,"like"